<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/complete-fix.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .director-hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 38, 71, 0.8), rgba(10, 38, 71, 0.8)), url('/images/school-hero.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 0 60px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .director-hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .director-message-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: var(--bg-cream);
        }

        .director-card {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
            background: white;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .director-image-container {
            flex: 0 0 350px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .director-image {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 5px solid white;
        }

        .director-image-accent {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: -15px;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-gold);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-gold);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .director-details {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .director-header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bg-cream);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .director-header h2 {
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .director-header h3 {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .director-details p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .director-signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        .director-contact-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--bg-cream);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .director-contact-info p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .director-card {
                padding: 30px;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .director-image-container {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
                max-width: 400px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="director-hero-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Director's Message</h1>
                    <p>Leadership that inspires excellence and integrity.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="director-message-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="director-card">
                        <div class="director-image-container">
                            <div class="director-image-accent"></div>
                            <img src="/images/Director_Image.jpeg" alt="Director Sumant Raj" class="director-image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="director-details">
                            <div class="director-header">
                                <h2>SUMANT RAJ</h2>
                                <h3>Director, N.R.K. Public School</h3>
                            </div>
                            <p>Dear Students, Parents, and Well-wishers,</p>
                            <p>It is my privilege to welcome you to N.R.K. Public School, an institution founded on the
                                pillars of quality education, moral integrity, and social responsibility. Our mission is
                                to provide an environment where every child feels inspired to reach their full
                                potential and emerge as a confident, compassionate leader of tomorrow.</p>
                            <p>In today's rapidly evolving world, education must go beyond conventional classroom
                                learning. At N.R.K. Public School, we emphasize a holistic approach that balances
                                academic excellence with sports, arts, and character building. We are dedicated to
                                providing the best facilities and a nurturing atmosphere for our students in rural Bihar
                                to ensure they are at par with global standards.</p>
                            <p>We believe that strong roots lead to a bright future. Our curriculum is designed to keep
                                students connected to their values while equipping them with modern skills like digital
                                literacy and scientific inquiry. Every student at our school is a unique individual, and
                                our faculty is committed to guiding them with care and expertise.</p>
                            <p>I am grateful for the trust parents have placed in us. We view education as a partnership
                                between the school and the home, and we encourage you to be active participants in your
                                child's journey. Together, we can shape the path toward a progressive and enlightened
                                society.</p>
                            <p>With best wishes,</p>
                            <div class="director-signature">
                                <strong>SUMANT RAJ</strong><br>
                                Director, N.R.K. Public School
                            </div>
                            <div class="director-contact-info">
                                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> <strong>Email:</strong>
                                    principal@nageshwaramtrust.org</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="call-to-action">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Embrace a Brighter Future</h2>
                    <p>Admissions are open for the upcoming academic session. Join the N.R.K. Public School community
                        today.</p>
                    <a href="/school/admissions" class="cta-button gold">Admission Details</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>